OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFive-day bank holiday in   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSri Lanka for debt         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frestructure                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sri Lanka began a five-day bank holiday
OL,6, from Thursday to allow the crisis-hit  
OL,7, nation to restructure $42bn (#33.2bn)  
OL,8, in domestic debt.                      
OL,10,FThe country is facing its worst        
OL,11,Feconomic crisis since it won           
OL,12,Findependence from the British in 1948. 
OL,14,FThere are fears that the government's  
OL,15,Frestructuring plan could lead to       
OL,16,Fvolatility in financial markets.       
OL,18,FDebt restructuring can involve the     
OL,19,Fextension of the period over which a   
OL,20,Floan is repaid.                        
